376 (a) The secretary may establish reasonable record fees
377 for the provision of a background check report, not to exceed
378 thirty dollars ($30). The record fee may be waived at the
379 discretion of the secretary.
380 (b) Additional costs may be assessed to a person or
381 entity requesting a background check for any of the following:
382 (1) The cost for a national criminal background check,
